      "en": "跳蚤市场: 46,131₽ | 物品价值: 18,397 | Mechanic报价: 10,302₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 64,191₽\n购买渠道 @ Mechanic 等级2 < 18,397₽\n购买渠道 @ Mechanic 等级2 < Prokill x2 | Σ ≈ 196,358₽\n购买渠道 @ Mechanic 等级3 < 61,128₽\n购买渠道 @ Mechanic 等级4 < 302,322₽\n购买渠道 @ Mechanic 等级4 < 电路板 x1 + Iridium x1 | Σ ≈ 160,417₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级2 < GP x44.41 | Σ ≈ 333,075₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级4 < GP x44.66 | Σ ≈ 334,950₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级3 < GP x73.87 | Σ ≈ 554,025₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级1 < GP x15 | Σ ≈ 112,500₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级3 < GP x39 | Σ ≈ 292,500₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级1 < CPU x3 + CPU风扇 x1 | Σ ≈ 75,271₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级4 < 威士忌 x3 + 伏特加 x1 | Σ ≈ 179,159₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级2 < 723$ ≈ 86,798₽\n购买渠道 @ Peacekeeper 等级4 < LEDX x1 | Σ ≈ 665,611₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级1 < 975$ ≈ 117,000₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < BEAR x6 | Σ ≈ 5,400₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < 2,313$ ≈ 277,560₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级4 < 丙烷 x1 + USEC x1 + TP-200 x1 | Σ ≈ 147,089₽\n\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Punisher - Part 5 @ Prapor\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Compensation for Damage - Collection @ Fence\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > Import ontrol @ Mechanic\n任务需要 x2 > Whats Your Evidence @ Peacekeeper\n任务需要 (✔) x1 > The Western Connection - Part 2 @ Skier\n\nThe Colt M4A1 carbine is a fully automatic variant of the basic M4 Carbine and was primarily designed for special operations use.\nHowever, U.S. Special Operations Command (USSOCOM) was soon to adopt the M4A1 for almost all special operations units, followed later by general introduction of the M4A1 into service with the U.S. Army and Marine Corps."
